headline: 3 Reasons to Sell VTRS and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a time it’s been for Viatris. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has increased by a massive 41.5%, reaching $13.07 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
